<paragraph id="0E66017A7764FF93B2F0FD96FB5AFC84" blockId="12.[151,1437,532,2023]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
The 
<typeStatus id="D162BFD87764FF93B2ABFD96FED4FDBF" box="[204,302,532,557]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">holotype</typeStatus>
for this taxon is part of the collection of the Brookline (
<collectingRegion id="CC1DCF987764FF93B1DBFD96FB9BFDBF" box="[956,1121,532,557]" country="United States of America" name="Massachusetts" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Massachusetts</collectingRegion>
) entomologist Frederick C. Bowditch held in the Museum of Comparative Zoology, University of Harvard. This species is so characteristic and with such a precise distribution that it should offer no problems for its identification. Moreover, Bowditch's description was detailed and accurate, so that a redescription is not really needed. However, I opted to redescribe the type here for uniformity and to add additional characters that have been consistently used in these revisions and missing in the original descriptions of most 
<taxonomicName id="C9D97AF97764FF93B0F1FD38FCE5FD41" authorityName="Chevrolat" authorityYear="1836" box="[662,799,698,723]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Calligrapha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="3CADDD687764FF93B0F1FD38FCE5FD41" box="[662,799,698,723]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Calligrapha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species. 
<bibRefCitation id="6A487C8B7764FF93B1EDFD38FAD5FD41" author="Montelongo, T. &amp; Gomez-Zurita, J." box="[906,1327,698,723]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="369 - 391" refId="ref57841" refString="Montelongo, T. &amp; Gomez-Zurita, J. (2013) Morphological and molecular characterization of a new Nearctic species of Calligrapha Chevrolat, 1836 (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae, Chrysomelinae) from Central Mexico. Proceedings of the Entomological Society of Washington, 115, 369 - 391. https: // doi. org / 10.4289 / 0013 - 8797.115.4.369" type="journal article" year="2013">Montelongo &amp; Gómez-Zurita (2013)</bibRefCitation>
provided with updated distribution and ecological data for this species in their comparison with 
<taxonomicName id="C9D97AF97764FF93B604FD5FFA6DFD67" authority="Gomez-Zurita" authorityName="Gomez-Zurita" authorityYear="2013" box="[1123,1431,732,757]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Calligrapha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="thermalis">
<emphasis id="3CADDD687764FF93B604FD5FFB14FD67" box="[1123,1262,732,757]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. thermalis</emphasis>
Gómez-Zurita
</taxonomicName>
; since there are no additions to locality data after that work, the list will not be repeated here.
</paragraph>
